Handy Flashlight: Privacy policy

This is an open source Android app developed by archemax. 
This app is available on Google Play.

I assure you that my app does not collect any personal data without your knowledge.

All data is created by the user and is stored on your device. 

Here is the Explanation of permissions. 
The list of permissions required by the app can be found in the AndroidManifest.xml file:

    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.CAMERA" />
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE" />
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE_CAMERA" />
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />

Yours sincerely, archemax.
